text: Albin Novšak (born 9 February 1915, date of death unknown) was a Slovenian ski jumper. He competed in the individual event at the 1936 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1915 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Slovenian male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Yugoslavia Category:Ski jumpers at the 1936 Winter Olympics Category:People from the Municipality of Bohinj
